export default {
  name: "AdminHome",

  },
  data() {
    return {

  methods: {},
  async mounted() {
    console.log(localStorage.getItem('authToken'));
    try {
      const response = await axios.get("http://127.0.0.1:5000/admin_home", {
        headers: {
          Authorization: `Token ${localStorage.getItem("authToken")}`,
        },

    } catch (error) {
        console.log(error.response)
    }
  },
};
</script>
